name: Winter Sun
description: There's something about this image that I can't get away from. I keep feeling the need to recreate it over and over and perhaps finally I have done her justice. Is it the look in her eyes? Or is it the rhythm of the lines or the coziness of her scarf half covering her mouth. I'm not sure, but I do hope that you can also bask in the warmth of the sun on your winter days.
